From: Takeshi Kihara <takeshi.kihara.df@renesas.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Feb 2017 21:27:32 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 1782/2066] arm64: dts: r8a7795-salvator-xs: Add Sound SRC
 support

This patch adds support of SRC in R-Car sound for This patch adds
support of SSI in R-Car sound for Salvator-X 2nd version board on
R8A7795 ES2.0 SoC.

Signed-off-by: Takeshi Kihara <takeshi.kihara.df@renesas.com>
[zou:Original patch taken from
git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/horms/renesas-bsp.git
 v4.9/rcar-3.5.1]
Signed-off-by: zou cao <cao.zou@windriver.com>
---
 .../arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a7795-salvator-xs.dts |    4 ++--
 1 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a7795-salvator-xs.dts b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a7795-salvator-xs.dts
index 9f2d665..ef1a133 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a7795-salvator-xs.dts
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/renesas/r8a7795-salvator-xs.dts
@@ -553,8 +553,8 @@
 
 	rcar_sound,dai {
 		dai0 {
-			playback = <&ssi0>;
-			capture  = <&ssi1>;
+			playback = <&ssi0 &src0>;
+			capture  = <&ssi1 &src1>;
 		};
 	};
 };
